# ------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Sample UnixTree configuration file
#
# The xt program will look for the following configuration files:
#	xt.rc
#	xt.rc.$TERM
# using the search path in XTPATH (if defined) or
# the default path of ".:~/.xt:<xt-system-directory>".
#
# Note that outside of quotes case, white space, "-", and "_" are ignored.
#
# This file duplicates all the defaults and follows the layout
# in the configuration screen.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------

